      "passage": "Desertification happens when fertile land slowly turns into desert because of dry weather and poor farming. Trees and grasses die first, leaving the soil bare and easy to blow away. Without plants, the ground loses water and nutrients, and farmers can no longer grow crops there. Many people are forced to leave their villages and search for new places to live and work.",
